snippet.title: Fledgling Manor | Official Trailer
snippet.description:
Buy on Steam now! https://store.steampowered.com/app/3238510/Fledgling_Manor/

Fledgling Manor is a supernatural horror visual novel from In Secret Places. Eight vampires compete to save their eternal unlives in a high-stakes reality show. Featuring an original soundtrack by kendall :3, eight characters to get to know and condemn to death, and half a dozen endings to discover.
